    "created_at": "2014-08-05T23:27:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-08-05T23:59:48Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Note that this also affects `expanding_*` functions, e. g. (in 0.14.1):\n``\nIn [4]: s = Series(range(10))\n\nIn [11]: expanding_mean(s, center=True)\nOut[11]:\n0    2.0\n1    2.5\n2    3.0\n3    3.5\n4    4.0\n5    4.5\n6    NaN\n7    NaN\n8    NaN\n9    NaN\ndtype: float64\n\nIn [12]: expanding_mean(s, min_periods=0, center=True)\nOut[12]:\n0    2.0\n1    2.5\n2    3.0\n3    3.5\n4    4.0\n5    4.5\n6    NaN\n7    NaN\n8    NaN\n9    NaN\ndtype: float64\n\n```\n```\n"
  },
